---


First — Why Noise Happens

Noise comes from:

Tiny white specks

Uneven lighting

Compression artifacts

Texture in background

Random sensor variation

After thresholding, all those become “objects”.

So the key idea is:

👉 Clean the image BEFORE detecting contours
👉 Clean the binary image AFTER thresholding